name: Semeru
description: On December 4th, 2021, Mount "Semeru" erupted accompanied by spewing hot clouds of avalanches on Saturday at around 15.00 WIB. Mount “Semeru” is a conical volcano in East Java, Indonesia. Mount "Semeru" is the highest mountain on the island of Java, with a peak "Mahameru", located at 3,676 meters above sea level.
